videos.description: Louisville's Asia Durr creates space with the crossover and converts the 3-pointer in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Durr knocks down 3-pointer off the crossover

videos.description: After missing her initial shot attempt, Louisville's Myisha Hines-Allen grabs the offensive rebound and goes up strong for a layup, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hines-Allen converts second-chance bucket

videos.description: Louisville's Myisha Hines-Allen dishes the ball to Sam Fuehring cutting down the lane for the layup.
videos.headline: Hines-Allen sets up Fuehring's lay-in

videos.description: Louisville's Arica Carter works the ball inside to Bionca Dunham for the tough lay-in, earning a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Dunham sinks tough layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Florida State's AJ Alix fires a pass inside to Shakayla Thomas for the layup in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Alix finds Thomas inside for the lay-in

videos.description: With time running low in the fourth quarter, Florida State's AJ Alix pulls up behind the arc and converts the 3-pointer, giving the Seminoles a 2-point lead.
videos.headline: Alix converts clutch go-ahead 3
